msgid ""
"You can access this command from the image menubar through "
"<menuchoice><guimenu><accel>L</accel>ayer</guimenu><guimenuitem>Layer "
"B<accel>o</accel>undary Size</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Der Menüeintrag kann aus dem Bildfenster erreicht werden: "
"<menuchoice><guimenu><accel>E</accel>bene</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Ebenen<accel>g</accel>röße</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

